---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12 prose">
		<h1 class="text-center text-6xl">
			<div class="noo mb-8">
				<a class="text-eu-blue no-underline" href="/">noo</a>
			</div>
			<div>Privacy Policy</div>
		</h1>
		<p>
			<strong>Effective date:</strong> February 22, 2025
		</p>
		<p>
			At <span class="noo">noo</span>, we believe privacy is a fundamental right. This website (noo.eu) is designed to respect your privacy by collecting as little data as possible.
		</p>

		<h2>What we collect</h2>
		<p>We do not collect personal data through this website.</p>
		<p>The only way we receive any information is if you email us directly at <a href="mailto:hello@noo.eu">hello@noo.eu</a>.</p>

		<h2>How we use your information:</h2>
		<p>If you email us:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>We will use your email address solely to respond to your inquiry.</li>
			<li>We will not share, sell, or distribute your email address to third parties.</li>
		</ul>
		
		<h2>Cookies & tracking</h2>
		<p>We do not use cookies, analytics tools, or any form of tracking.</p>

		<h2>Your rights</h2>
		<p>If you wish to:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Access, correct, or delete your email conversation,</li>
			<li>Withdraw consent for further communication,</li>
		</ul>
		<p>Simply email us at
			<a href="mailto:hello@noo.eu">hello@noo.eu</a>, and we'll comply promptly.</p>

		<h2>Contact us</h2>
		<p>For any privacy-related questions, reach out at <a href="mailto:hello@noo.eu">hello@noo.eu</a>.</p>
	</main>
</Layout>
